Note on the accent layer:
The accent information in this dictionary was assigned using UniDic
(National Institute for Japanese Language and Linguistics). UniDic is
distributed under its own license (GPL/LGPL/BSD triple license). Factual
accent-core positions are not generally subject to copyright, but please
